WEBVTT

00:01:28.360 --> 00:01:30.016
as well as others.

00:01:30.040 --> 00:01:32.696
And it's about identities
we just assume that we have

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:34.960
without thinking too much about them.

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:40.136
But our responses
to questions of identity and origin

00:01:40.160 --> 00:01:44.920
have substantial
social and political importance.

00:01:45.640 --> 00:01:49.496
We see the wars, the rages of identity
going on all around us.

00:01:49.520 --> 00:01:53.976
We see violent religious,
national and ethnic disputes.

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:58.640
And often the conflict is based
on old stories of identity

00:01:59.600 --> 00:02:01.136
and belonging